text.tspan: Push a button, key, turn a knob, wiggle something...
Explicitly set to none to avoid accidental push
To remove a mapping, one has to scroll a list.
Row vs Item: click whitespace on row to select for removal, click text to bind event/set function.
Send keystroke is only a workaround for apps not supporting the mapping API.
Send keystroke is done in two steps. Selecting the function and then assigning the keystroke to send.
